and weird locations of the UK.</p>","updated":1780937254,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/75681"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3637527","name":"Hertfordshire"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3637528","name":"Hampshire"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3637528"},"show":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/75681","name":"Weird Britain"}}},{"id":3648323,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3648323/katie-price-nothing-to-hide-1x01-becoming-jordan","name":"Becoming Jordan","season":1,"number":1,"type":"regular","airdate":"2026-07-08","airtime":"21:00","airstamp":"2026-07-08T20:00:00+00:00","runtime":70,"rating":{"average":null},"image":null,"summary":"<p>A profile of one of Britain's most enduring celebrity figures, combining previously unseen footage with first-hand testimonies from Katie and those closest to her.</p>","show":{"id":91632,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/91632/katie-price-nothing-to-hide","name":"Katie Price: Nothing to Hide","type":"Documentary","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"In Development","runtime":null,"averageRuntime":70,"premiered":"2026-07-08","ended":null,"officialSite":null,"schedule":{"time":"","days":[]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":65,"network":{"id":1750,"name":"Sky Documentaries","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"},"officialSite":"https://www.sky.com/watch/sky-documentaries"},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":null,"thetvdb":null,"imdb":null},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/629/1573210.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/629/1573210.jpg"},"summary":"<p>For 30 years, Katie Price has turned her private life into public spectacle. The nation thinks they know her - but <b>Katie Price: Nothing to Hide</b> will challenge them to look again.</p><p>Katie Price: Nothing to Hide, a Sky Original four-part series brings a documentary lens to Katie's story, combining extraordinary unseen footage with first-time testimony to deliver a revealing portrait of one of Britain's most enduring celebrity figures.</p><p>This archive-led retrospective goes beyond the headlines, with intimate access to Katie and those closest to her - some for decades, some for pivotal moments, and some whose stories have never been told - to candidly examine the consequences of placing herself, and those around her, at the centre of public attention.</p><p>Since emerging as her alter ego ‘Jordan' on Page 3 of The Sun in 1996, Katie Price has become one of the most photographed women of her generation. Her life has played out across newspapers, magazines, reality television and social media - from marriages, motherhood and multi-million pound contracts to scandal, cosmetic surgery, bankruptcy and betrayal.  </p>","updated":1782402123,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/91632"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3648323","name":"Becoming Jordan"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3648323"},"show":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/91632","name":"Katie Price: Nothing to Hide"}}},{"id":3656910,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3656910/love-island-13x33-episode-33","name":"Episode 33","season":13,"number":33,"type":"regular","airdate":"2026-07-08","airtime":"21:00","airstamp":"2026-07-08T20:00:00+00:00","runtime":65,"rating":{"average":null},"image":null,"summary":null,"show":{"id":11363,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/11363/love-island","name":"Love Island","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":["Romance"],"status":"Running","runtime":65,"averageRuntime":64,"premiered":"2015-06-07","ended":null,"officialSite":"https://www.itv.com/watch/love-island/2a3697","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7.2},"weight":98,"ne